sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as LlmResponseProcessor
    participant T as TerminalManager
    participant W as Webview chat.js
    participant P as ChatViewProvider
    participant L as LlmService

    R->>T: enqueue(파일토큰)
    T->>T: executeFileOpFromToken(token)
    alt delete ENOENT
      T->>T: 스킵 후 다음 항목
    else 쓰기/수정 실패
      T-->>W: priorityErrorPrompt 전송
      W->>P: postMessage(priorityErrorPrompt)
      P->>L: handleUserMessageAndRespond(우선 처리)
    end
